": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "a short piece of copper wire"}, "description": {"value": "You point your finger toward a creature within range and whisper a message. The target (and only the target) hears the message and can reply in a whisper that only you can hear.\n\nYou can cast this spell through solid objects if you are familiar with the target and know it is beyond the barrier. Magical silence, 1 foot of stone, 1 inch of common metal, a thin sheet of lead, or 3 feet of wood blocks the spell. The spell doesn't have to follow a straight line and can travel freely around corners or through openings."}, "classes": {"value": ["artificer__eb_", "artificer__revised_", "bard", "sorcerer", "fighter", "rogue", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.618894"}}}, {"resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"id": "bane", "name": {"value": "Bane"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_1"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_enchantment"}, "ritual": {"value": false}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "30 feet"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 1 minute"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "a drop of blood"}, "description": {"value": "Up to three creatures of your choice that you can see within range must make Charisma saving throws. Whenever a target that fails this saving throw makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target must roll a d4 and subtract the number rolled from the attack roll or saving throw."}, "higher_level_description": {"value": "When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st."}, "classes": {"value": ["bard", "cleric"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.605174"}}}, {"resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"id": "friends", "name": {"value": "Friends"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_0"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_enchantment"}, "ritual": {"value": false}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "Self"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 1 minute"}, "verbal": {"value": false}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "a small amount of makeup applied to the face as this spell is cast"}, "description": {"value": "For the duration, you have advantage on all Charisma checks directed at one creature of your choice that isn't hostile toward you. When the spell ends, the creature realizes that you have used magic to influence its mood and becomes hostile toward you. A creature prone to violence might attack you. Another creature might seek retribution in other ways (at the GM's discretion), depending on the nature of your interaction with it."}, "classes": {"value": ["bard", "sorcerer", "warlock", "blood_hunter", "fighter", "rogue", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.612698"}}}, {"resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Enhance Ability"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_2"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_transmutation"}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "Touch"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 1 hour"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "fur or a feather from a beast"}, "description": {"value": "A creature you touch gains one of the following effects until the spell ends:\n\n- Bear's Endurance: The target has advantage on Constitution checks. It also gains 2d6 temporary hit points, which are lost when the spell ends.\n\n- Bull's Strength: The target has advantage on Strength checks, and its carrying capacity doubles.\n\n- Cat's Grace: The target has advantage on Dexterity checks. It also doesn't take damage from falling 20 feet or less if it isn't incapacitated.\n\n- Eagle's Splendor: The target has advantage on Charisma checks.\n\n- Fox's Cunning: The target has advantage on Intelligence checks.\n\n- Owl's Wisdom: The target has advantage on Wisdom checks"}, "higher_level_description": {"value": "When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 2nd."}, "classes": {"value": ["artificer", "artificer__eb_", "artificer__revised_", "bard", "cleric", "druid", "sorcerer"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "effects": {"value": [{"resource_id": "effect", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Bear's Endurance"}, "trigger_type": {"value": "active"}, "trigger_condition": {"value": {"resource_id": "trigger_condition_or", "stats": {"id": "002f1897-8260-49ca-90de-fce51fceecb8"}}}, "type": {"value": "advantage"}, "advantage_stat": {"value": "$character.constitution_modifier"}, "id": "7b38a3e8-78c9-4c6e-8282-c2a64adc4009"}}, {"resource_id": "effect", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Bull's Strength"}, "trigger_type": {"value": "active"}, "trigger_condition": {"value": {"resource_id": "trigger_condition_or", "stats": {"id": "7cacb6cd-08a1-404a-95a3-ca2cfe41ede6"}}}, "type": {"value": "advantage"}, "id": "ea5fb51b-aa2b-47d7-8372-99f17a9092ae"}}, {"resource_id": "effect", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Cat's Grace"}, "trigger_type": {"value": "active"}, "trigger_condition": {"value": {"resource_id": "trigger_condition_or", "stats": {"id": "14a22589-99c2-4105-b174-588648b5eaa6"}}}, "type": {"value": "advantage"}, "advantage_stat": {"value": "$character.dexterity_modifier"}, "id": "57d98fc1-bba6-45ad-909f-81b36209ae73"}}, {"resource_id": "effect", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Eagle's Splendor"}, "trigger_type": {"value": "active"}, "trigger_condition": {"value": {"resource_id": "trigger_condition_or", "stats": {"id": "6b8bd863-a376-4ce2-9bc9-21b97cef748d"}}}, "type": {"value": "advantage"}, "advantage_stat": {"value": "$character.charisma_modifier"}, "id": "07be147d-398a-4504-89db-2ab3d15b09d0"}}, {"resource_id": "effect", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Fox's Cunning"}, "trigger_type": {"value": "active"}, "trigger_condition": {"value": {"resource_id": "trigger_condition_or", "stats": {"id": "f659c716-6a37-4965-b82a-e2f401d82df6"}}}, "type": {"value": "advantage"}, "advantage_stat": {"value": "$character.intelligence_modifier"}, "id": "e6c4baeb-e8d9-4707-aff4-b1a1820c95cc"}}, {"resource_id": "effect", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Owl's Wisdom"}, "trigger_type": {"value": "active"}, "trigger_condition": {"value": {"resource_id": "trigger_condition_or", "stats": {"id": "9d09e866-cedc-4251-a1e2-a0e3b39cda0b"}}}, "type": {"value": "advantage"}, "advantage_stat": {"value": "$character.wisdom_modifier"}, "id": "56e06412-6a35-4a03-8b2d-f30ddb5cdf8f"}}]}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.651728"}, "id": "enhance_ability"}}, {"resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"id": "mending", "name": {"value": "Mending"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_0"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_transmutation"}, "ritual": {"value": false}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 minute"}, "range": {"value": "Touch"}, "duration": {"value": "Instantaneous"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "two lodestones"}, "description": {"value": "This spell repairs a single break or tear in an object you touch, such as a broken key, a torn cloak, or a leaking wineskin. As long as the break or tear is no longer than 1 foot in any dimension, you mend it, leaving no trace of the former damage.\n\nThis spell can physically repair a magic item or construct, but the spell can\u2019t restore magic to such an object."}, "classes": {"value": ["artificer__eb_", "artificer__revised_", "bard", "cleric", "druid", "sorcerer", "fighter", "rogue", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.618748"}}}, {"resource_id